References to Department of Human Services have been updated to Services Australia.
References to Department of Human Services have been updated to Services Australia.

All existing customers will be prompted to setup and use a myGov PIN to open their app. The myGov PIN is a universal PIN used to access other apps registered to their myGov account. To set up the app, customers must enter their myGov account sign in details. This registers the app to their myGov account. If they don't have a myGov PIN, the app will prompt them to create one.

Customers will be able to use their email address or a myGov user name to register the app to their myGov account.
